"""
xrp — sovereign XRP terminal wallet + point of sale

Usage:
  xrp init                          Generate new wallet
  xrp balance                       Show balance
  xrp receive [--amount N] [--label TEXT]   Show receive QR
  xrp send <address> <amount> [--tag N] [--memo TEXT]
  xrp watch [--amount N] [--tag N] [--on-payment CMD]
  xrp history [--limit N]
  xrp address                       Print your address
  xrp export                        Show seed phrase (careful)
  xrp node <url>                    Set custom XRPL node
  xrp pos [--port N]                Launch browser-based point of sale
"""

